            <title>[HBASE-7880] HFile Recovery/Rewrite Tool</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/HBASE-7880</link>
                <project id="12310753" key="HBASE">HBase</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Sometimes is useful to have a tool to migrate files from a new version to an old version (e.g. convert a new XYZ encoded/compressed file to an old &quot;uncompressed&quot; format)&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;also it will be useful to been able to recover an hfile from a corrupted state. (e.g. trailer missing/broken, ...) &lt;br/&gt;
The &quot;user&quot; can provide the information about the file (compression &amp;amp; co) and  try to recover as much as possible from the file by reading data blocks.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
